        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Steve James was born in Hampton, Virginia, USA. He is a director and producer, known for <a href="/title/tt0110057?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">Hoop Dreams</a> (1994), <a href="/title/tt2382298?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">Life Itself</a> (2014) and <a href="/title/tt0334416?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">Stevie</a> (2002). He is married to <a href="/name/nm1321021?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk4">Judy James</a>.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0416945/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Hampton,+Virginia,+USA&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Hampton, Virginia, USA</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
                   </td>
