    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-personal-quote" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Personal Quote:</h4>
(On Harlan County USA) There've been many documentaries over the years that have powerfully impacted me. I think this one came along at the time when I was more interested in being a feature filmmaker than a documentary filmmaker. So it came along at the beginning of a process of moving from an interest in feature film to documentaries, and that's where my career has taken me. It came along at ...                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0416945/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_qt_sm#quotes"
>See more</a> 
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
